==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: lǎowài

===Etymology===
[[老]] (''lao'', "old") + [[外]] (''wai'', "foreign")

===Noun===
'''[[老]][[外]]'''

# (''pejorative'') [[foreigner]]
# {{figurative}} a Chinese person who acts western or does not understand a specific topic

====Synonyms====
* (''foreigner''): [[鬼佬]] (Cantonese: ''gweilo'')
* (''a Chinese person who acts western''): [[banana]]

====Usage notes====
Using the term to refer to foreigners is controversial and may be perceived as exclusionist.

